data.reasoningText:
The package is just a library (DLL), it doesn't have build targets that auto-generate an entry point. In xUnit.net v3, the test project needs an explicit entry point. Looking at the xUnit.net v3 documentation, the test project needs a `Program.cs` like this:

```csharp
var testAssembly = typeof(SomeTestClass).Assembly;
await Xunit.Runner.InProcess.ConsoleClient.Run(testAssembly);
```

